<emphasis id="B902EAE17E1CFF91FF74D957FF43FEAD" box="[136,239,356,377]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="148">Etymology</emphasis>
: The specific epithet 
<emphasis id="B902EAE17E1CFF91FE42D957FDC2FEAD" box="[446,622,356,377]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="148">
“ 
<taxonomicName id="4C764D707E1CFF91FE39D957FDCBFEAD" authorityName="Chaiwan &amp; K. D. Hyde" authorityYear="2021" box="[453,615,356,377]" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Glomerellaceae" genus="Colletotrichum" kingdom="Fungi" order="Glomerellales" pageId="5" pageNumber="148" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="dracaenigenum">dracaenigenum</taxonomicName>
”
</emphasis>
refers to the host genus 
<emphasis id="B902EAE17E1CFF91FCA5D957FC13FEAD" box="[857,959,356,377]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="148">
<taxonomicName id="4C764D707E1CFF91FCA5D957FC17FEAD" box="[857,955,356,377]" class="Liliopsida" family="Asparagaceae" genus="Dracaena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="5" pageNumber="148" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Dracaena</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
from which the 
<typeStatus id="54CD88517E1CFF91FBA1D957FB1DFEAE" box="[1117,1201,356,378]" pageId="5" pageNumber="148">holotype</typeStatus>
was collected.
</paragraph>
